<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871216-0056 </DOCNO><HL> Perception Technology Shares</HL><DD> 12/16/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> PCEPBUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK) </IN><DATELINE> CANTON, Mass.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Perception Technology Inc. said its board approved the buy-back of as many as 500,000 common shares from time to time on the open market.    The maker of interactive voice response systems said it currently has about 3.6 million shares outstanding. </TEXT></DOC>